---
import Form from "./Form.astro";
---

<footer class="bg-primary pt-12 pb-96 md:pb-40 relative">
  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row px-10 justify-center gap-40 lg:gap-10">
    <div class="max-w-lg flex flex-col gap-3">
      <h2 class="text-section-header text-secondary">Contacto</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-16 text-base-content-dim text-paragraph">
        <p>
          Si te interesa lo que escribo y querés comunicarte podés hacerlo por
          mail o por instagram.
        </p>
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/assets/arrows/arrow-2.svg"
            alt="arrow mail"
            class="absolute rotate-90 -right-28 top-40 lg:-top-14 lg:-right-10 lg:rotate-0"
          />
          <p>Acá te dejo un formulario para enviarme un mail más facilmente.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative group/container">
          <img
            src="/assets/arrows/arrow-1.svg"
            alt="arrow instagram"
            class="absolute rotate-12 md:rotate-0 top-20 md:top-10 md:left-10"
          />
          <a href="#" class="absolute top-36 left-32 md:top-28 md:left-44">
            <img src="/assets/logos/mdi_instagram.svg" alt="instagram logo" />
          </a>
          <p>Y un link a Instagram. Gracias por leer!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <Form />
  </div>
  <img
    src="/assets/plants/plant-3.svg"
    alt="plant"
    class="absolute bot-[700px] md:top-[410px] xl:top-40 right-0"
  />
</footer>
